item.title: CVE-2023-1426|2024-08-02T05:49:11.415Z -- unknown -- wp%20tiles
item.description: The WP Tiles WordPress plugin through 1.1.2 does not ensure that posts to be displayed are not draft/private, allowing any authenticated users, such as subscriber to retrieve the titles of draft and privates posts for example. AN attacker could also retrieve the title of any other type of post.
